e%20said%20he%20shifted%20from%20only%20applying%20to%20remote%20roles%20to%20considering%20hybrid%20ones%2C%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20networking%20played%20a%20key%20role%2C%20since%20a%20former%20colleague%20helped%20him%20land%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EJoseph%20Leemon%2C%20a%2044-year-old%20from%20Rochester%20Hills%2C%20Michigan.%20His%20previous%20employment%2C%20offer%2C%20application%20count%2C%20and%20identity%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Elaid%20off%20from%20my%20last%20job%20on%20October%203%2C%202023.%20On%20October%204%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiter-who-has-written-over-700-resumes-best-advice-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eupdated%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20redownloaded%20all%20the%20job%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20I've%20applied%20to%20roughly%202%2C000%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sought%20outside%20counsel%20from%20recruiters%20or%20others%20in%20managerial%20positions.%20I%20also%20tried%20out%20three%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9-writing%20services%2C%20spending%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20on%20them%20with%20no%20results.%20I%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eused%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20really%20didn't%20like%20what%20I%20read%20from%20it.%20My%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20got%20to%20the%20point%20where%20it%20just%20sort%20of%20felt%20like%20some%20random%20keywords%20that%20were%20hopefully%20going%20to%20be%20caught%20by%20the%20ATS%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20last%20job%20was%20as%20an%20agent%20services%20specialist%20at%20a%20real-estate%20tech%20company.%20I%20wasn't