bitcoin%20was%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20greater%20fool%20theory%2C%20or%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20case%20for%20buying%20a%20particular%20asset%20is%20that%20there%20will%20always%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreater%20fool%26quot%3B%20who%20will%20pay%20more%20than%20you%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20view%2C%20the%20problem%20with%20gold's%20big%20rally%20is%20that%20investors%20see%20the%20gains%20and%20believe%20there%20is%20intrinsic%20value%20like%20a%20stock.%20It's%20an%20incorrect%20narrative%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20gold%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20%5Bwill%20say%5D%20it's%20just%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20Ricchiutii%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20isn't.%20Stocks%20represent%20growth%20and%20value.%20You%20own%20a%20percentage%20of%20that%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERicchiuti%20said%20he%20understands%20the%20drive%20to%20diversify%20amid%20historically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-crash-fears-overblown-valuation-metrics-1999-comparison-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elofty%20stock%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20lingering%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20but%20he's%20steadfast%20in%20his%20belief%20that%20gold%20doesn't%20have%20much%20use%20beyond%20being%20a%20vehicle%20for%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20an%20inflation%20hedge%E2%80%94perhaps%20gold's%20most%20frequently%20touted%20use%E2%80%94the%20stock%20market%20might%20be%20the%20better%20place%20for%20investors%20to%20hide%20while%20fiat%20currencies%20inflate%20their%20value%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20long-term%20investor%20and%20you%20believe%20in%20the%20story%20and%20you%20believe%20in%20management%2C%20I%20think%20over%20long%20periods%20of%20time%2C%20stocks%20will%20do%20much%2C%20much%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Ricchiuti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-pric