20Google.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI's%20new%20app%20directory%20and%20software%20signal%20its%20intent%20to%20attract%20developers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDevelopers%20face%20challenges%20with%20rapid%20innovation%20and%20platform%20choices%20in%20the%20AI%20space.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-saas-software-tools-including-openhouse-hr-sales-support-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20trying%20to%20become%20the%20next%20big%20tech%20platform%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20rolling%20out%20a%20host%20of%20new%20products%2C%20tools%2C%20and%20features%20to%20appeal%20to%20developers%2C%20including%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-just-launched-app-store-taking-aim-apple-google-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-flavored%20App%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Murby%2C%20whom%20I%20met%20while%20waiting%20in%20a%20long%20line%20to%20get%20into%20OpenAI's%20DevDay%20conference%20last%20week%2C%20agrees.%20He's%20the%20director%20of%20business%20development%20at%20Devpost%2C%20which%20helps%20developers%20participate%20in%20hackathons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20Murby%20how%20OpenAI%20is%20appealing%20to%20developers%20and%20what%20it%20still%20has%20to%20do%20to%20challenge%20Apple%20and%20Google.%20This%20Q%26amp%3BA%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20clarity%20and%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20From%20what%20you%20witnessed%20at%20DevDay%2C%20is%20OpenAI%20now%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20developers%3F%20Or%20does%20it%20still%20have%20work%20to%20do%20here%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20deserve%20massive%20credit%20for%20changing%20the%20world%20with%20the%20first%20generative%20AI%20consumer%20product%20and%20providing%20the%20model%20that%20powered%20GitHub%20Copilot%2C%20but%20it's%20far%20from%20won.%20From%20our%20vantage%20point%20at%20Devpost%2C%20they%20are%20in%20a%20race%20for%20developer%20engagement%20and%20trust%2C%20and%20that's%20exactly%20the%20problem%20we%20help%20companies%20solve.%20(Full%20disclosure%2C%20we%20work%20with%20OpenAI%20and%20their%20competitors.)%20The%20speed%20of%20innovation%20means%20that%20developers%20have%20numerous%20options%2C%20and%20the%20companies%20that%20win%20are%20those%20that%20can%20cut%20through%20the%20noise%20and%20get%20developers'%20hands%20on%20their%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20Take%20me%20inside%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20developer.%20Why%20would%20they%20be%20clamoring%20to%20engage%20with%20OpenAI%3F%20What's%20the%20payoff%20for%20developers%20to%20build%20things%20on%20this%20nascent%2Femerging%20platform%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20modern%20developer's%20toolkit%20is%20astonishingly%20rich.%20GenAI%20offers%20a%20direct%20payoff%20for%20most%20developers%2C%20assisting%20them%20with%20everything%20from%20bug%20fixes%20to%20feature%20development.%20This%20speed%20and%20utility%20mean%20that%20they%2C%20and%20their%20executives%2C%20want%20to%20leverage%20this%20technology%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20competing%20to%20be%20a%20developer's%20default%20choice.%20They've%20provided%20top-quality%20models%20and%20continue%20to%20expand%20what's%20available%20in%20the%20API%2C%20but%20the%20real%20game-changer%20is%20the%20new%20app%20directory%20and%20SDK.%20This%20is%20a%20clear%20signal%20that%20OpenAI%20is%20attempting%20to%20create%20a%20platform%20where%20developers%20can%20find%20users%20and%20earn%20revenue%2C%20much%20like%20Apple%20did%20with%20the%20App%20Store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20What%20are%20the%20drawbacks%20for%20developers%20building%20on%20OpenAI's%20platform%3F%20What%20did%20you%20see%20on%20Monday%20that%20changes%20this%20situation%2C%20if%20anything%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20such%20fierce%20competition%20and%20an%20intense%20pace%20of%20innovation%2C%20the%20primary%20challenge%20for%20developers%20is%20simply%20keeping%20up.%20They%20face%20a%20strategic%20dilemma%3A%20do%20they%20go%20all-in%20on%20one%20platform%2C%20or%20do%20they%20spread%20their%20bets%20across%20multiple%20tools%3F%20This%20is%20compounded%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20new%20AI%20benchmarks%20are%20surpassed%20almost%20weekly%20by%20different%20competitors%2C%20and%20internal%20security%20and%20IT%20teams%20can%20only%20ingest%20so%20many%20new%20tools%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20as%20the%20race%20is%20on%2C%20developers%20are%20utilizing%20these%20tools%20both%20at%20work%20and%20in%20their%20free%20time.%20This%20is%20why%20hackathons%20are%20so%20critical%E2%80%94they%20provide%20a%20dedicated%20space%20for%20companies%20to%20test%20tools%20and%20for%20developers%20to%20gain%20hands-on%20experience%2C%20all%20while%20providing%20valuable%20feedback.%20This%20is%20our%20specialty%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20key%20component%20of%20a%20successful%20developer%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20what%20we%20saw%20on%20Monday%2C%20OpenAI%20is%20making%20a%20significant%20statement%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20be%20the%20next%20platform.%20Their%20investments%20in%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20new%20app%20directory%2C%20and%20a%20new%20coding%20agent%20all%20signal%20that%20they%20are%20here%20to%20stay%20and%20want%20to%20be%20the%20default%20choice%20for%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20How%20far%20away%20is%20OpenAI%20from%20challenging%20the%20current%20major%20platforms%2C%20Apple%20iOS%2C%20Google%20Android%20etc%3F%20What's%20missing%20or%20different%20here%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comparison%20to%20Apple%20and%20Google%20is%20a%20red%20herring.%20What%20OpenAI%20is%20doing%20is%20not%20a%20traditional%20platform%20play%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20straight-up%20attempt%20to%20build%20the%20dominant%20conversational%20operating%20system%20of%20the%20future.%20The%20platform%20is%20moving%20from%20the%20device%20to%20the%20conversation%20itself.%20This%20is%20a%20massive%20new%20challenge%3A%20creating%20a%20community%20of%20developers%20that%20will%20build%20on%20top%20of%20this%20conversational%20platform%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20device.%20That's%20a%20new%20frontier%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20incredibly%20fortunate%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it%20and%20see%20how%20it%20unfolds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ%3A%20What%20else%20struck%20you%20from%20DevDay%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjony-ive-ideas-openai-family-ai-devices-sam-altman-design-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJony%20Ive%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20really%20stuck%20with%20me.%20To%20paraphrase%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20we%20run%20this%20new%20generation%20of%20technology%20through%20the%20last%20generation's%20interfaces%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20brilliantly%20simple%20and%20profound%20thought%20that%20makes%20me%20incredibly%20excited%20to%20find%20out%20what%20they%20are%20working%20on.%20I%20just%20really%20wish%20they%20had%20told%20us!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3Ehere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-next-big-tech-platform-developers-apple-google-devpost-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3