%20past%20week%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20implemented%20another%20force%20reduction%20across%20federal%20agencies%2C%20impacting%20over%204%2C100%20federal%20workers%2C%20as%20the%20government%20shutdown%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFired%20federal%20workers%20could%20lose%20progress%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-program-pslf-education-department-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPublic%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20forgives%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20a%20federal%20worker%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20student%20loans%3F%20Share%20your%20story%20with%20this%20reporter%20at%20asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20or%20via%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20payments%20to%20count%20toward%20PSLF%2C%20a%20borrower%20must%20be%20working%20for%20a%20qualifying%20employer%2C%20like%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20when%20the%20payments%20are%20made.%20That%20means%20that%20a%20federal%20worker%20impacted%20by%20the%20RIF%20will%20not%20receive%20credit%20toward%20PSLF%20unless%20they%20get%20hired%20at%20a%20different%20employer%20that%20would%20qualify%20for%20the%20program.%20Once%20they%20get%20a%20new%20qualifying%20employer%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20where%20they%20left%20off%20with%20their%20PSLF%20payments.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarolyn%20Fast%2C%20director%20of%20higher%20education%20policy%20at%20the%20left-leaning%20think%20tank%20The%20Century%20Foundation%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20recommends%20borrowers%20affected%20by%20the%20federal%20cuts%20document%20their%20PSLF%20payment%20count%20now%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20have%20copies%20of%20it%20to%20avoid%20any%20issues%20down%20the%20road%20when%20they%20have%20to%20verify%20their%20payments%20to%20receive%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20borrowers%20who%20are%20at%20the%20120%20payment%20mark%20should%20apply%20for%20forgiveness%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20regulation%20talks%20about%20how%20you%20need%20to%20be%20at%20the%20eligible%20employment%20when%20you%20apply%20for%20the%20forgiveness%20after%20you%20make%20the%20amount%20of%20payments%2C%26quot%3B%20Fast%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it'd%20be%20important%20to%20do%20that%20while%20you're%20still%20a%20federal%20worker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20PSLF%20buyback%20process%20could%20also%20be%20beneficial%20for%20some%20federal%20workers%2C%20Fast%20said.%20Buybacks%20allow%20borrowers%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20back%26quot%3B%20months%20spent%20in%20deferment%20or%20forbearance%20periods%20by%20making%20payments%20equal%20to%20what%20they%20would%20have%20owed%20at%20the%20time%2C%20if%20those%20payments%20would%20enable%20them%20to%20reach%20the%20120%20payment%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20workers%20with%20over%2010%20years%20of%20public%20service%20but%20who%20have%20not%20yet%20received%20forgiveness%20should%20consider%20whether%20they%20might%20qualify%20for%20a%20buyback%2C%20Fast%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20who%20received%20a%20RIF%20notice%20were%20placed%20on%20administrative%20leave%20beginning%20October%2010%2C%20according%20to%20the%20notices%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20and%20the%20terminations%20will%20become%20effective%20in%20early%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20student-loan%20repayment%20system%20is%20undergoing%20major%20changes.%20The%20Department%20of%20Education%20held%20negotiations%20in%20July%20on%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-borrowers-react-debt-relief-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elimit%20PSLF%20eligibility%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20department%20said%20could%2